@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_psmftd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin(((v1 + 0.23 + v0 + 0.28) - (v2 + 0.17 * tmp + 0.13)))
    tmp = tmp
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.abs((tmp + 0.22 * v1 + 0.86)))
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.12)))
    v2 = tmp
    v1 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
